sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant B as Browser
  participant API as Express API
  participant V as voteController
  participant A as anomalyDetector
  participant DB as Supabase
  participant E as eventBus

  B->>API: POST /api/votes/init { browserToken }
  API->>API: zod validate · IP rate-limit
  API->>API: HMAC sign(browserToken, ts, nonce)
  API-->>B: 200 { voteToken, ttlSec: 300 }

  B->>API: POST /api/votes { projectId, browserToken, voteToken }
  API->>API: zod validate · IP rate-limit
  API->>V: castVote
  V->>V: verifyVoteToken (HMAC, expiry, browser-token match)
  V->>DB: SELECT projects WHERE id=?
  V->>DB: SELECT votes WHERE browser_token=?
  alt already voted
    V-->>B: 409 already voted
  else fresh
    V->>A: scoreVote(ip, ua, browserToken)
    A-->>V: { score, severity, reasons }
    V->>DB: INSERT INTO votes(...)
    V->>DB: rpc increment_vote_count(projectId)
    V-)A: recordFlag (best-effort, async)
    V-)E: broadcast 'vote.cast'
    V-->>B: 201 { projectId, flagged }
  end
